item.title: CVE-2020-3843|2024-08-04T07:44:51.216Z -- apple -- ios-1
item.description: A memory corruption issue was addressed with improved input validation. This issue is fixed in iOS 12.4.7, watchOS 5.3.7. A remote attacker may be able to cause unexpected system termination or corrupt kernel memory.
